          From laptop to production
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          See how OpenData takes you from local development to scaled production
          with the same tools and the same operational model at every step.
        </p>
      </div>

      <Demo client:visible />

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <div class="inline-block rounded-xl bg-accent/5 border border-accent/20 px-6 py-4 max-w-2xl">
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-semibold text-text">Everything you saw</span> uses the same storage engine,
            same config system, same CLI tools, same metrics. That's the OpenData advantage.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Database Cards Section -->
