        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
          All OpenData databases share a common storage engine, infrastructure layer,
          and operational tooling built on SlateDB.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <CodeBlock title="architecture" code={archCode} />

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
